<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>{{ site_title }} - アスオラ最新情報まとめ</title>
<meta name="description" content="アストラエ・オラティオ（アスオラ）関連の最新まとめ記事を新着順に集約するアンテナサイト。">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#1a1a2e">
<link rel="canonical" href="{{ site_url }}/">
<link rel="alternate" type="application/rss+xml" title="{{ site_title }}" href="{{ site_url }}/feed.xml">
<meta property="og:type" content="website">
<meta property="og:title" content="{{ site_title }}">
<meta property="og:description" content="アスオラ関連の最新まとめ記事を集約するアンテナサイト。">
<meta property="og:url" content="{{ site_url }}/">
<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary">
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    background: #0f0f1a;
    color: #e8e8f0;
    font-family: "Hiragino Sans", "Yu Gothic UI", "Meiryo", system-ui, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 15px;
  }
  header.site-head {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #2d1b4e 50%, #1a1a2e 100%);
    border-bottom: 2px solid #7b5fc7;
    padding: 18px 16px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  header.site-head h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: #ffd700;
    text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(123, 95, 199, 0.6);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  header.site-head .tagline {
    margin-top: 4px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #b0a8d0;
  }
  nav.site-nav {
    background: #161628;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #2a2a3e;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  nav.site-nav a {
    color: #c8b5ff;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin: 0 10px;
  }
  nav.site-nav a:hover { color: #ffd700; text-decoration: underline; }

  main {
    max-width: 880px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 16px;
  }
  .meta-bar {
    color: #888aa0;
    font-size: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    text-align: right;
  }
  ul.entries {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }
  ul.entries li.entry {
    background: #16162a;
    border: 1px solid #2a2a44;
    border-left: 3px solid #7b5fc7;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: border-left-color 0.15s, background 0.15s;
  }
  ul.entries li.entry:hover {
    border-left-color: #ffd700;
    background: #1c1c34;
  }
  .entry .title {
    margin: 0 0 6px;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .entry .title a {
    color: #ffe8a8;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .entry .title a:visited { color: #c4b8d8; }
  .entry .title a:hover { color: #fff; text-decoration: underline; }
  .entry .meta {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #8a8aab;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .entry .meta .source {
    background: #2d1b4e;
    color: #c8b5ff;
    padding: 1px 8px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-size: 11px;
  }
  .entry .summary {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #aaaac8;
    margin: 4px 0 0;
  }

  footer {
    margin-top: 32px;
    padding: 20px 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid #2a2a3e;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #6a6a88;
  }
  footer a { color: #c8b5ff; text-decoration: none; }
  footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    header.site-head h1 { font-size: 18px; }
    .entry .title { font-size: 15px; }
    main { padding: 10px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="site-head">
  <h1>⚔ {{ site_title }} ⚔</h1>
  <div class="tagline">アストラエ・オラティオ関連まとめ・新着RSSアンテナ</div>
</header>

<nav class="site-nav">
  <a href="{{ main_blog_url }}/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">公式まとめブログ</a>
  <a href="{{ site_url }}/feed.xml">このサイトのRSS</a>
</nav>

<main>
  <div class="meta-bar">最終更新：{{ generated_at }}　／　収録 {{ entries|length }} 件</div>

  <ul class="entries">
    {% for e in entries %}
    <li class="entry">
      <div class="meta">
        <span class="source">{{ e.source_name }}</span>
        <span class="time">{{ e.published_jst_str }}</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="title"><a href="{{ e.link }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ e.title }}</a></h2>
      {% if e.summary %}
      <p class="summary">{{ e.summary }}</p>
      {% endif %}
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</main>

<footer>
  <p>
    <strong>{{ site_title }}</strong> ／ 関連サイト：
    <a href="{{ main_blog_url }}/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">アスオラまとめ速報（asuora.com）</a>
  </p>
  <p>本サイトは各まとめサイトの公開RSSをもとに新着順で表示しています。記事本文の権利は各配信元に帰属します。</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
